ocaml-ssl
------------------------------------------
OCaml bindings for libssl to secure connections by using 
ssl encryption in your sockets.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.1-1
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  ocaml-3.11.2-1
  openssl-0.9.8l-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.19.51-1
  cygport-0.9.80-1
  flexdll-0.20-1
  gcc-core-4.3.4-3
  make-3.81-2

Canonical website:
  http://savonet.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/savonet/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ocaml-ssl-0.4.4-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ocaml-ssl-0.4.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ocaml-ssl-0.4.4-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ocaml-ssl-0.4.4-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 0.4.4-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin 1.7.


Cygwin port maintained by:
